      <title>Ubuntu 22.04 常用命令</title>
      <link href="/2024/03/01/Ubuntu-22-04-%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/"/>
      <url>/2024/03/01/Ubuntu-22-04-%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>本文记录 Ubuntu 22.04 下一些常用的命令</p><h2 id="ssh"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#ssh">#</a> SSH</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token comment"># 连接到服务器</span><span class="token function">ssh</span> marshwallen@172.20.20.144<span class="token comment"># 从服务器下载文件到指定目录（文件或文件夹）</span><span class="token function">scp</span> root@127.20.36.88:~/test.zip ~/Desktop<span class="token function">scp</span> <span class="token parameter variable">-r</span> root@127.20.36.88:~/test ~/Desktop<span class="token comment"># 查看历史连接用户</span><span class="token builtin class-name">cd</span> /var/loglast<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="文件操作"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#文件操作">#</a> 文件操作</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token comment"># 压缩</span><span class="token function">tar</span> <span class="token parameter variable">-vcf</span> test.tar ./test<span class="token comment"># 解压</span><span class="token function">tar</span> <span class="token parameter variable">-xvf</span> test.tar ./test<span class="token comment"># 列出文件夹及大小</span><span class="token function">ls</span> <span class="token parameter variable">-l</span><span class="token function">du</span> <span class="token parameter variable">-h</span> --max-depth<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token number">1</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="环境变量"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#环境变量">#</a> 环境变量</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token comment"># 修改</span><span class="token function">vim</span> ~/.bashrc<span class="token comment"># 应用修改</span><span class="token builtin class-name">source</span> ~/.bashrc<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="应用安装-更新"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#应用安装-更新">#</a> 应用安装、更新</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token comment"># apt安装</span><span class="token function">sudo</span> <span class="token function">apt</span> <span class="token function">install</span> xxx<span class="token comment"># apt卸载</span><span class="token function">sudo</span> <span class="token function">apt-get</span> remove xxx<span class="token function">sudo</span> <span class="token function">apt-get</span> autoremove<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="conda"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#conda">#</a> Conda</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token comment"># 创建环境</span>conda create <span class="token parameter variable">-n</span> xxx <span class="token assign-left variable">python</span><span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token number">3.7</span><span class="token comment"># 激活环境</span>conda activate xxx<span class="token comment"># 查看conda列表</span>conda <span class="token function">env</span> list<span class="token comment"># 删除环境</span>conda <span class="token function">env</span> remove <span class="token parameter variable">-n</span> xxx<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="screen"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#screen">#</a> Screen</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token comment"># 创建终端</span><span class="token function">screen</span> 或 <span class="token function">screen</span> <span class="token parameter variable">-S</span> xxx<span class="token comment"># 查看终端</span><span class="token function">screen</span> <span class="token parameter variable">-ls</span><span class="token comment"># 恢复终端</span><span class="token function">screen</span> <span class="token parameter variable">-r</span> xxx<span class="token comment"># 杀死终端</span><span class="token function">screen</span> <span class="token parameter variable">-S</span> xxx <span class="token parameter variable">-X</span> quit <span class="token comment"># 杀死前20个screen</span><span class="token function">screen</span> -ls<span class="token operator">|</span><span class="token function">awk</span> <span class="token string">'NR>=2&amp;&amp;NR&lt;=6&#123;print $1&#125;'</span><span class="token operator">|</span><span class="token function">awk</span> <span class="token string">'&#123;print "screen -S "$1" -X quit"&#125;'</span><span class="token operator">|</span><span class="token function">sh</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
      
