      <title>Ubuntu 22.04 维护小记</title>
      <link href="/2024/03/01/Ubuntu-22-04-%E7%BB%B4%E6%8A%A4%E5%B0%8F%E8%AE%B0/"/>
      <url>/2024/03/01/Ubuntu-22-04-%E7%BB%B4%E6%8A%A4%E5%B0%8F%E8%AE%B0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="重装-nvidia-显卡驱动"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#重装-nvidia-显卡驱动">#</a> 重装 NVIDIA 显卡驱动</h2><h3 id="问题背景"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#问题背景">#</a> 问题背景</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">Failed to initialize NVML: Driver/library version mismatch<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>故障原因：通过 apt 命令安装或更新的显卡驱动版本号与原驱动版本号不一致而导致掉驱动</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token comment"># 查看已安装的显卡驱动</span>dpkg <span class="token parameter variable">-l</span> <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token function">grep</span> nvidia<span class="token comment"># 查看本地使用的显卡驱动版本信息</span><span class="token function">cat</span> /proc/driver/nvidia/version<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>正常情况下，两者查到的版本号理应一致。</p><h3 id="解决方案"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#解决方案">#</a> 解决方案</h3><p>可通过卸载并重装显卡驱动解决。</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token comment"># 1 卸载旧版驱动</span><span class="token function">sudo</span> <span class="token function">apt-get</span> purge nvidia*<span class="token function">sudo</span> <span class="token function">apt-get</span> autoremove<span class="token comment"># 2 添加 NVIDIA 的ppa源</span><span class="token function">sudo</span> add-apt-repository ppa:graphics-drivers/ppa<span class="token comment"># 3 安装对应的显卡驱动（如535）</span><span class="token function">sudo</span> <span class="token function">apt-get</span> <span class="token function">install</span> nvidia-driver-535<span class="token comment"># 4 重启系统</span><span class="token function">sudo</span> <span class="token function">reboot</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h3 id="参考文章"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#参考文章">#</a> 参考文章</h3><p>[1] <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/ykf173/article/details/116230368">https://blog.csdn.net/ykf173/article/details/116230368</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
